Art,<br><br>
Thanks for the nice compliment. I think that the most important thing is to be understood - not necessarily in agreement.<br><br>
Yes, my purpose - my &quot;agenda&quot; is to level the playing field - to make room for everyone at the table. <br><br>
I think all who have participated in this forum - especially those who have hung in there for almost a year have all presented themselves honestly. If we tried to scratch everyone's back and not cause any waves, then we would be insincere - learning (and teaching) nothing.<br><br>
You have paid me very high compliments, allow me to do likewise to you. Art, my paisano, I could sleep very peacefully knowing you were in FDC up on the Firebase. And, most certainly I could think of no other person I would rather be &quot;stuck&quot; with than you, my *brother* of choice.<br><br>
As for your speaking out in anger no problem here - because you have always tempered your anger with soothing words of encouragement to others. <br><br>
Don't ever give up.<br><br>
Peace, Tom
